1
00:00:32,340 --> 00:00:35,940
=Ruan Xiaofeng's Royal Love Quest=

2
00:00:36,020 --> 00:00:38,900
=Episode 11=

3
00:00:45,150 --> 00:00:46,290
This is it.

4
00:00:49,900 --> 00:00:50,890
Tell me

5
00:00:51,190 --> 00:00:52,820
who's behind you.

6
00:00:53,300 --> 00:00:54,579
Why do they need this?

7
00:00:54,580 --> 00:00:55,860
How can you be so certain

8
00:00:55,980 --> 00:00:57,570
this is what I'm looking for?

9
00:00:58,110 --> 00:01:00,060
I've been by her side for three years.

10
00:01:00,150 --> 00:01:02,180
I know all her secrets.

11
00:01:02,830 --> 00:01:04,180
Forgive me

12
00:01:04,910 --> 00:01:06,620
for I can't answer your questions.

13
00:01:14,020 --> 00:01:15,980
Stay here. I'll go check outside.

14
00:01:56,990 --> 00:01:58,010
Don't chase them.

15
00:02:00,630 --> 00:02:02,010
Didn't I tell you to stay inside?

16
00:02:03,350 --> 00:02:05,010
I'm worried about you.

17
00:02:06,070 --> 00:02:08,220
Are you all right?

18
00:02:09,110 --> 00:02:10,250
It's minor.

19
00:02:11,180 --> 00:02:13,620
I believe
this is what we're looking for.

20
00:02:30,830 --> 00:02:32,130
Is this Imperial Concubine Wan?

21
00:02:41,180 --> 00:02:43,810
In the 17th year
of Emperor Jihuan's reign,

22
00:02:44,430 --> 00:02:47,300
the sixth day of the third month,
at Bixiao Tower.

23
00:02:48,340 --> 00:02:51,690
It draws the view
before my mother fell.

24
00:02:55,740 --> 00:02:57,690
Who's the woman next to Her Highness?

25
00:02:58,620 --> 00:03:00,339
She's my mother's maidservant,

26
00:03:00,340 --> 00:03:02,580
Ren Dong, from Jiangnan.

27
00:03:03,230 --> 00:03:05,429
It's said that my mother

28
00:03:05,430 --> 00:03:06,970
saved her life from danger,

29
00:03:07,670 --> 00:03:10,460
and ever since, she became
my mother's trusted servant.

30
00:03:16,270 --> 00:03:18,090
She possessed sword dance skills,

31
00:03:18,300 --> 00:03:21,220
which my mother then used
to regain the Emperor's favor.

32
00:03:36,460 --> 00:03:38,740
She was also skilled
in crafting fragrances.

33
00:03:38,830 --> 00:03:41,619
The Soothing Scent
Liu Yu mentioned that day

34
00:03:41,620 --> 00:03:43,060
was her creation.

35
00:03:43,670 --> 00:03:46,810
Dayuan found that scented sachet
at Bixiao Tower.

36
00:03:47,710 --> 00:03:49,250
So that means

37
00:03:49,550 --> 00:03:52,180
Ren Dong was the last person
by Her Highness's side before she died.

38
00:03:52,710 --> 00:03:54,340
If we can find Ren Dong,

39
00:03:54,870 --> 00:03:56,300
everything will become clear.

40
00:03:57,110 --> 00:03:58,300
I searched for her,

41
00:03:58,830 --> 00:04:01,810
but there was no trace of her.
We don't know if she's alive or dead.

42
00:04:08,340 --> 00:04:09,810
Are there no other methods

43
00:04:10,460 --> 00:04:12,850
besides this?

44
00:04:13,620 --> 00:04:15,580
We need more clues.

45
00:04:17,140 --> 00:04:19,700
If His Majesty could grant
the permission,

46
00:04:20,670 --> 00:04:21,780
maybe...

47
00:04:22,820 --> 00:04:23,669
What's wrong?

48
00:04:23,670 --> 00:04:25,490
- Maybe...
- Li Rui. What's wrong?

49
00:04:26,550 --> 00:04:27,490
What's wrong with you?

50
00:04:29,140 --> 00:04:30,490
Let me see your wound.

51
00:04:33,740 --> 00:04:34,970
There's poison on the dart.

52
00:04:36,470 --> 00:04:38,820
Hold on. I'll get a physician.

53
00:04:39,740 --> 00:04:40,700
Don't go.

54
00:04:42,380 --> 00:04:44,650
All right. I won't go.

55
00:04:47,060 --> 00:04:48,490
Will you be heartbroken

56
00:04:49,260 --> 00:04:50,940
if I die?

57
00:04:53,380 --> 00:04:54,610
I... No.

58
00:04:54,940 --> 00:04:55,819
I'm just afraid...

59
00:04:55,820 --> 00:04:57,050
At a time like this,

60
00:04:58,300 --> 00:05:00,900
just admit it if you like me.

61
00:05:04,820 --> 00:05:05,850
Yes,

62
00:05:08,030 --> 00:05:09,220
I like you.

63
00:05:16,300 --> 00:05:17,730
Your story.

64
00:05:20,450 --> 00:05:23,760
♪Love goes on like an endless flow♪

65
00:05:23,850 --> 00:05:29,560
♪I gaze afar
across the river of memories♪

66
00:05:30,610 --> 00:05:34,089
♪The wind caresses your face♪

67
00:05:34,090 --> 00:05:37,360
♪Feelings of the past
linger deep inside♪

68
00:05:37,370 --> 00:05:43,360
♪Tears feel surreal
as laughter echoes on♪

69
00:05:44,210 --> 00:05:47,649
♪Amidst the twinkling starry sky♪

70
00:05:47,650 --> 00:05:50,929
♪Your graceful figure
bathed in moonlight♪

71
00:05:50,930 --> 00:05:56,800
♪The moment I turn back,
I will never forget this sight♪

72
00:05:57,770 --> 00:06:01,209
♪If love overwhelms me♪

73
00:06:01,210 --> 00:06:03,929
♪How could I ever resist?♪

74
00:06:03,930 --> 00:06:09,440
♪I only wish for you to be well♪

75
00:06:10,810 --> 00:06:14,129
♪May the blowing wind
and falling rain♪

76
00:06:14,130 --> 00:06:17,649
♪Never dampen
the corner of your robe♪

77
00:06:17,650 --> 00:06:21,089
♪May you stay afloat♪

78
00:06:21,090 --> 00:06:24,489
♪Through the ups and downs♪

79
00:06:24,490 --> 00:06:27,769
♪May you sleep peacefully♪

80
00:06:27,770 --> 00:06:32,800
♪Unaware of the dawn
and free of worries♪

81
00:06:38,230 --> 00:06:39,669
It's a deep cut.

82
00:06:39,670 --> 00:06:42,020
But the poison was removed in time.

83
00:06:42,110 --> 00:06:43,820
His Highness is all right now.

84
00:06:46,870 --> 00:06:48,170
Thank you, sir.

85
00:06:57,850 --> 00:06:59,640
(I'm in the mountains
while you're in the lake.)

86
00:06:59,640 --> 00:07:01,360
(But love hides within the clouds.
Xiaofeng)

87
00:07:04,910 --> 00:07:06,220
Princess Zhaoning,

88
00:07:06,430 --> 00:07:09,020
your love poems

89
00:07:09,140 --> 00:07:10,780
are unbearable.

90
00:07:11,030 --> 00:07:12,580
Since I'm you now,

91
00:07:12,700 --> 00:07:14,090
I'll burn it.

92
00:07:14,180 --> 00:07:15,029
Sorry.

93
00:07:15,030 --> 00:07:17,730
You'll thank me for it one day.

94
00:07:28,470 --> 00:07:29,460
Mother.

95
00:07:30,500 --> 00:07:31,460
Mother.

96
00:07:32,350 --> 00:07:33,410
Mother.

97
00:07:47,700 --> 00:07:48,970
Xiaofeng.

98
00:07:51,870 --> 00:07:53,170
Xiaofeng.

99
00:07:57,236 --> 00:07:58,410
Xiaofeng.

100
00:08:01,130 --> 00:08:04,480
♪And carries them to the riverbank♪

101
00:08:05,410 --> 00:08:10,160
♪The scattered past
drifts further with each step♪

102
00:08:10,250 --> 00:08:13,240
♪Too shallow, too faint♪

103
00:08:15,570 --> 00:08:19,320
♪Memories still follow♪

104
00:08:20,050 --> 00:08:23,960
♪Entwined, refusing to let go♪

105
00:08:24,690 --> 00:08:27,969
♪I don't want this freedom♪

106
00:08:27,970 --> 00:08:33,000
♪As long as you don't go♪

107
00:08:33,610 --> 00:08:37,920
♪Like drifting sand
slipping through my grip♪

108
00:08:38,102 --> 00:08:42,120
♪The tighter I hold, the more I lose♪

109
00:08:42,530 --> 00:08:45,849
♪Spring goes, autumn comes,
as day and night take turns♪

110
00:08:45,850 --> 00:08:50,729
♪I guard my obsession♪

111
00:08:50,730 --> 00:08:55,880
♪Let me be drunk in dreams
and ache when sober♪

112
00:08:56,090 --> 00:09:00,320
♪Every single word is
etched into my heart♪

113
00:09:00,530 --> 00:09:03,249
♪In the silent world♪

114
00:09:03,250 --> 00:09:07,960
♪Only a true heart can be heard♪

115
00:09:09,010 --> 00:09:13,929
♪Let me endure this tormenting pain♪

116
00:09:13,930 --> 00:09:20,280
♪And blend you into my soul♪

117
00:09:20,970 --> 00:09:23,369
♪Defying fate♪

118
00:09:23,370 --> 00:09:31,480
