lose our jobs.

140
00:10:42,260 --> 00:10:43,229
That's right.

141
00:10:43,230 --> 00:10:44,829
People will do anything for money.

142
00:10:44,830 --> 00:10:46,259
We

143
00:10:46,260 --> 00:10:48,589
had no choice but to switch sides
to Yeyang Pavilion.

144
00:10:48,590 --> 00:10:49,659
Switch sides?

145
00:10:49,660 --> 00:10:51,829
Hurry up. Do you want to lose your job?

146
00:10:51,830 --> 00:10:54,130
- Your Highness. Wishing you the best of luck.
- We want our jobs.

147
00:10:55,070 --> 00:10:56,869
Your Highness, good luck.

148
00:10:56,870 --> 00:10:59,090
Your Highness, farewell.

